{"tid":1049342,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"遊客腳尖上的港鐵　組成美麗風景線　網民嘆為觀止","createTime":"2019-03-06T08:00:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T09:02:34.000Z","uid":39464,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"66fc6f19084a3ac333c54bee5bbf77ee4ece7348","tid":1049342,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T08:00:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190306/photo/bkn-20190306153416753-0306_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190306155259\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190306%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190306153416753-0306_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190306155259&h=cdab18a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n踎低休息舒服啲？有網民星期三（6日）在Facebook群組「香港花生友」上載相片，有疑似內地客在港鐵月台蹲下候車，惹來網民狂派嬲。 <br />\n<br />\n從相中可見，有5名男女使出獨特的等車方法，「排排蹲」在月台黃線後，望着列車駛入港鐵站，其中一名中年漢還找到柱子作「背墊」，狀甚舒適。旁邊一名身穿迷彩外套的男子更以行李篋作椅，坐着玩手機。 <br />\n<br />\n他們整齊的隊形令網民嘆為觀止︰「企一陣隻腳會跛㗎咩？踎喺度隻腳仲攰啦」、「充分流露生活習慣同風格」、「係咪屙緊屎呀」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190306/bkn-20190306153416753-0306_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190306%2Fbkn-20190306153416753-0306_00822_001.html&d=iefYBA3dMTKG%2BriJzBrQhRZmCTjK%2FM6Kxb2TK%2FvXQ0I%3D&h=bdfb44ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190306/bkn-20190306153416753-0306_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"68d35d28e55a75fe932fc99f65f1719887078324","tid":1049342,"uid":191762,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T08:12:40.000Z","msg":"其實踎低咪仲攰"},{"pid":"9a18e0bae56458acc6154cedcaf88d50395fff57","tid":1049342,"uid":19978,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T08:14:43.000Z","msg":"坐行李箱都算，話哂係佢自己，中意坐爛去都唔關人事，但其他真係有礙市容"},{"pid":"f70b46fc14384d773e0611997ffdab669a24fb0f","tid":1049342,"uid":117200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9a18e0bae56458acc6154cedcaf88d50395fff57","tid":1049342,"uid":19978,"like":4,"dislik